Inner Hidden 5/100

Inner Hidden is a multimedia project in which the author deals with the issue of mental illness through video, photography and sound.

A series of 100 photos of long exposures, which started on July 2nd, 2018. and was completed on October 25th, 2018. Is done by the method of sudden hand movements through Samsung Galaxy Core 2 mobile phone and Instagram application.
